{"ts": "2026-06-07T22:35:38.960979+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "---\n\n## Module Structure of the Spring Boot Java Template\n\nThis is a **multi-module Gradle project** (named `spring-boot-java-template`) that organizes a Spring Boot application into logical module groups. Each group has a clear responsibility and is designed to scale with the project.\n\n### 🔷 **Core** — Domain logic and the main application\n| Submodule | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `core:core-api` | **The only executable module** (Spring Boot app). Houses domain services and exposes APIs. Serves as the entry point and framework setup layer. |\n| `core:core-enum` | Contains shared enums used by `core-api` and other external modules — keeps shared constants in one place. |\n\n### 🌐 **Clients** — External system integration\n| Submodule | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `clients:client-example` | Demonstrates HTTP communication with external services using **Spring Cloud OpenFeign**. |\n\n### 💾 **Storage** — Data persistence\n| Submodule | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `storage:db-core` | Provides database connectivity, demonstrated with **MySQL** via **Spring Data JPA**. |\n\n### 🛠️ **Support** — Cross-cutting concerns\n| Submodule | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `support:logging` | Centralized logging setup with **distributed tracing** and **Sentry** integration. |\n| `support:monitoring` | Service monitoring and observability support. |\n\n### 🧪 **Tests** — Testing infrastructure\n| Submodule | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `tests:api-docs` | Generates API documentation using **Spring REST Docs** with AsciiDoc. |\n\n---\n\n### Visual Dependency Summary\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│              core:core-api                   │  ← Executable entry point\n│          (Domains, APIs, Framework)          │\n├──────────┬──────────┬───────────────────────┤\n│ core:    │ storage: │  clients:             │\n│ core-enum│ db-core  │  client-example       │\n├──────────┴──────────┴───────────────────────┤\n│              support:logging                 │  ← Cross-cutting\n│              support:monitoring              │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│              tests:api-docs                  │  ← Test support\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n### Key Design Principles\n- **Dependency versions** are centralized in `gradle.properties` and loaded via `build.gradle`\n- **Runtime profiles** (`local`, `local-dev`, `dev`, `staging`, `live`) support different deployment environments\n- **Test task groups** (`unitTest`, `contextTest`, `restDocsTest`, `developTest`) allow selective test execution on CI\n- A **Git hook** enforces Spring Java Format linting on every commit", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 633, "prompt_tokens": 7232, "total_tokens": 7865, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 16, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 3840, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.000662872, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.000485632, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00017724}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780871729-h3RJbFJio24rxhkcNkub", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea43a-12bc-7843-8570-95f20a13fcc4-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 7232, "output_tokens": 633, "total_tokens": 7865, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 3840}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 16}}}}]}}}
